  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nYannick used /skill-creator to build a 'dev' skill that automatically handles complex coding tasks in the Y-OS ecosystem. The skill integrates Claude API with flexible model selection (Sonnet 3.5/3.7), includes Y-OS stack knowledge, and enables Manus to automatically inject project context and manage development workflows.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nCreate an automated development skill using the skill-creator tool to streamline coding tasks within the Y-OS development environment\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nConfigured and deployed a dev skill with flexible Claude model selection, universal Y-OS stack support, and automatic project context injection by Manus\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [skill] dev skill — Automated development agent skill for Y-OS projects with Claude integration\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Use flexible Claude model selection instead of fixed claude-sonnet-4-5\n- Keep universal Y-OS stack configuration rather than project-specific stacks\n- Enable automatic project context injection by Manus rather than manual input\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Skill creator workflow was efficient and direct\n- Structured questioning clarified key configuration choices\nDiscoveries:\n\n- Dev skill can auto-activate on complex coding tasks\n- Manus can orchestrate context injection and error handling automatically\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Test the dev skill with actual Y-OS development tasks\n- Monitor skill performance and refine model selection logic\n---\nUID: baOukAjGMsgUKnIy1RF9YT | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0115\n"
}